<section id="message" class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative elements with anime-inspired motifs -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-20 wine-accent"></div>
  
  <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 w-64 h-64 opacity-10 z-0">
    <!-- One Piece inspired hat silhouette -->
    <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M85,35c0,0-15-25-35-25S15,35,15,35s-5,15,0,30s20,25,35,25s30-10,35-25S85,35,85,35z" fill="#722F37"/>
      <path d="M50,10c-20,0-35,25-35,25h70C85,35,70,10,50,10z" fill="#D11D3A"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  
  <div class="absolute -bottom-5 -left-5 w-32 h-32 opacity-10 rotate-12 z-0">
    <!-- Chemistry flask icon -->
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M9 3H15M10 3V8L4 16.5C3.4 17.3 3.5 18.5 4.2 19.2C4.9 19.9 6 20 7 19.4L8.5 18.5C9 18.2 9.5 18 10 18H14C14.5 18 15 18.2 15.5 18.5L17 19.4C18 20 19.1 19.9 19.8 19.2C20.5 18.5 20.6 17.3 20 16.5L14 8V3" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-dark-800/90 backdrop-blur-md p-8 md:p-12 rounded-xl border border-wine-800/40 shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif mb-4 chemistry-border inline-block">My Message to You</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
          My dearest love,
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-6">
          As we celebrate another year together, I wanted to take a moment to reflect on our journey. Every day with you has been a blessing, filled with laughter, love, and countless memories that I will cherish forever.
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-6">
          Your passion for chemistry and food engineering inspires me. Your love for anime, especially One Piece and Nana, brings so much joy and personality to our relationship. And just like the daisies you adore, you bring brightness and warmth to my life.
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-6">
          We've navigated through life's challenges together, supporting each other every step of the way. Thank you for being my partner, my best friend, and my greatest adventure.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-wine-300 mb-2">
          Happy Anniversary!
        </p>
        
        <p class="font-serif italic">
          With all my love,<br>
          [Your Name]
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Small Nana-inspired element -->
      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <div class="inline-block opacity-80">
          <!-- Simple Nana inspired icon -->
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z" fill="#FF69B4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>